com.tplmaps3d

Class IconFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tplmaps3d.IconFactory

  • public class IconFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides built in methods to set default icon or load bitmap from different sources including resources, drawable, assets etc.

    Returns Icon object to set shape background via Marker.setIcon(Icon)
